The following issue is being redeemed via the
company's call option:  Issuer:              Steinway Musical Instruments Inc (LVB) 
Coupon:             7 percent
Maturity:           March 1, 2014
Redemption Amount:  $67.506 million
Redemption Price:   100 percent
Amount Remaining:   Fully Retired
Security ID:        USU85858AB12
Effective Date:     July 15, 2013
 